<p>The preferences dialog contains shortcut button for these folders.</p>
<section>
<title>Scripts</title>
<p>These are JavaScript files places in the <code>scripts</code> folder inside the app folder. The JS code in these files is injected into the web app. This can be used to provide integration functionality to webapps which don't support fogger out of the box.</p>

</section>
<section>
<title>Styles</title>
<p>These are CSS stylesheet applied to the webapp. This allows use to easily change the look and feel of the webapps.</p>
</section>

